Weapon fire from Galaxor begins to rattle Abominus' massive frame, and 
the pressure begins to push him backwards, grinding against the cold 
earth. His front smoking, he begins to stand himself up, after being 
riddled with blasts. "Gruar rrrrrrr, grrrrrrrr" he emits in his 
emotionless voice.
